::Battera::

She stands still and looks at him. "I...I was contacted on my link 
about a bot named Unicron.  I was told he is on his way here." She 
smiled slightly. "I..ah..just passing it along."  She was about to 
turn away when it clicked inher mind that he said he was the 
commander.  She couldn't help but smile. "Your the commander here? Oh 
that's great.  I've been meaning to talk to you for a long time."
